    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a YANG data model for Source Address
   Validation (SAV) base. The model serves as a base framework for
   configuring and managing an SAV subsystem, including SAV rule and
   SAV Tables, and expected to be augmented by other SAV technology
   models accordingly. Additionally, this document also specifies the
   model for the SAV Static application.</t>
